text: Adelaide Harriet Boddam-Whetham was an archer from Great Britain. She was born on 9 December 1860 and died on 20 September 1954. Boddam-Whetham competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Adelaide Boddam-Whetham == References == Category:1860 births Category:1954 deaths Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain
